snippet.title: FUMES pre-alpha v0.1 Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam page:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1920430/FUMES/

Arm your vehicle with deadly weapons and roam endless wastelands in this fast-paced car combat game. Collect upgrades for your car to melt enemies and bosses in this bizarre world. Retro vibe. Retro cars. Retro gameplay!
